## Workflow

### Feature Development

```
1. PRD created and reviewed
2. @architect creates technical design
3. @developer implements in phases
4. @reviewer checks each phase
5. @tester adds test coverage
6. Final review and merge
```

### Bug Fixing

```
1. Bug report received
2. @developer investigates and proposes fix
3. @reviewer validates fix doesn't introduce regressions
4. @tester adds regression test
5. Merge and deploy
```

